      "snowpackStructure": {
        "comment": "The surface of the snowpack is generally characterised by alternating areas of erosion interspersed with areas of accumulation; in many areas there are hard surface crusts, some of which are hidden. Near the ridges, the wind over the past few days has led to the formation of snow overhanging mass. Weak layers exist in the snowpack in particular on shady slopes."
